Package: gepabds
Title: Gene Expression Profiler for Single-Cell RNA-seq Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Medha", "Vijayanand", , "medha.vijayanand@stjude.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides tools for analyzing and visualizing gene expression in SingleCellExperiment objects using single-cell RNA-seq data. The package
        supports inquiring about gene sets, computing per-cell-type expression statistics, calculating gene specificity scores using the Gini coefficient, and generating visualizations 
        that include violin plots and co-expression scatter plots. It also includes functionality to export expression summaries and specificity metrics for downstream analysis or CLI use. 
        The package is based on the Muraro human pancreatic single-cell RNA-seq dataset.
